## Project
SCW Villaments RWA Community Portal.

Stack: Next.js App Router, TypeScript, CSS Variables, SWR, NextAuth v5, googleapis.

## Key references
- Product requirements: SCW_Villaments_Portal_PRD_v1.2.pdf
- Design system: design-system.html
- Type definitions: src/types/index.ts
- Sheets client: src/lib/sheets.ts

## Rules
- Use strict TypeScript and avoid `any`.
- Keep Google service account access server-side only.
- Use only CSS token variables from `src/app/globals.css`.
- Protect write APIs with session and role checks.
- Return `{ error: string }` payloads for API failures.
